def build_user_agent(extra=""):
    agent = "{} (python {}; {}-{}) {}".format(

        platform.python_version(),
        platform.machine(),
        platform.system(),
        (extra or "")
    )
    agent = agent.strip()
    if APPEND_USER_AGENT:
        agent += " {}".format(APPEND_USER_AGENT)
    return agent
